    dc:description "Fig. 1. Friesea posada sp. nov., holotype male (RO-Fr3-IBB). (A) Habitus and dorsal chaetotaxy; (B) Fourth antennal segment; (C) Labium; (D) Tibiotarsal chaetotaxy and claw of leg III; (E) Chaetotaxy of abdominal sterna II-VI and ventral tube. A and E, scale bars = 0.1 mm. B-D, scale bars = 0.01 mm." ;
